message:
Hi Bob
I hope you are doing good. I am excited to present you with an opportunity to purchase my product. I am offering it to you with 12000 dollars. I think it is a fair price. let me know what you think.
best 
Robyn
Hey Robyn, thanks for the offer.  $12000 is a bit higher than I'm comfortable with right now. I'm willing to pay $9500 for the product. Let me know what you think.
